              "content": "=You are a cybersecurity SOC analyst. Analyze the following security log/alert and respond ONLY with valid JSON in this exact structure:\n\n{\n  \"summary\": \"1-2 sentence plain-language summary of what happened\",\n  \"severity\": \"low|medium|high|critical\",\n  \"incident_type\": \"e.g. brute_force, malware, phishing, unauthorized_access, data_exfiltration, other\",\n  \"affected_entities\": {\n    \"ip_addresses\": [],\n    \"usernames\": [],\n    \"hostnames\": []\n  },\n  \"indicators_of_compromise\": [],\n  \"recommended_action\": \"short recommended next step for the SOC team\",\n  \"confidence\": \"low|medium|high\"\n}\n\nLog content:\n{{ $json.data }}"
